interfaces

Interface ITestCase

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExcelTestCase

    public interface ITestCase
    Model used by the framework to allow for various types of Non-coded test design like Excel spreadsheets and JSON files This Interface models a Test Case and includes methods for getting information about a Test Case
    Author:
    Mathew Carrigan
